    "summary": "Cancellation of AI agent running request",
    "description": {
      "type": "doc",
      "version": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\uD83E\uDDE0 Overview"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The project \u003c!--comment_start:cme7mgpq200u8m0zrotqoqb8u--\u003efocuses\u003c!--comment_end:cme7mgpq200u8m0zrotqoqb8u--\u003e on implementing a feature that allows users to cancel an ongoing AI agent call directly from the user interface (UI). This feature aims to enhance user control by enabling the cancellation of requests both in the UI and on the backend, where the gRPC stream is managed using betterproto as a gRPC server."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\uD83C\uDFAF Goals"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Achieve seamless cancellation of AI agent requests from the UI, ensuring both frontend and backend processes are terminated."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Provide clear user feedback on the cancellation status to enhance user satisfaction."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Support multiple concurrent cancellations without performance degradation."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
